ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparnt cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL: Streptavidin-coated microparticles, 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.

R2 Anti-IgE-Ab~Ru(bpy)2+3 (black cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL: Monoclonal anti-IgE antibody (mouse) labeled with ruthenium complex 5.5 mg/L; phosphate buffer 85 mmol/L, pH 6.5; preservative.
